12-18\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2022-09-15\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised provenance\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2026-01-19\" who=\"#DD\">Dmitry Dundua's lemmatizations were added from source CoNLL-U files\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2026-01-19\" who=\"#RC\">Robert Crellin integrated lemmatizations into EpiDoc using PyEpiDoc and associated scripts\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2026-02-09\" who=\"#RG\">tagged names and persons\u003C/change>\n            \u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic003448_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic003448.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#SK\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>\u003Cw n=\"5\">Ἀσκλη\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\" break=\"no\"/>πιάδη\u003C/w>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Cw n=\"10\">χαῖρε\u003C/w>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"simple-lemmatized\" resp=\"#DD #RC\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"5\" lemma=\"Ἀσκληπιάδης\">Ἀσκληπιάδη\u003C/w>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"10\" lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε\u003C/w>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text of Cordano 2005\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>Asklepiades, farewell!\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>The text implies the vocative + salutation formula which is found several times at Mineo, and\n                    reproduced in the latin epitaph engraved on the reverse of this stone (\u003Cref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003447\">ISic003447\u003C/ref>). The text is said to come from Monte Catalfaro, c.3km NE of Mineo.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Messina\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1970\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>30 n.16 tav.11.3\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/59PEX25M\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001439\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001439\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Cordano\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2005\u003C/date>\n                        \u003Ccite